original_title: Dora the Explorer: It's a Party
overview: Four festive adventures from the tv show Dora the Explorer. The main episode is "Daisy, la Quinceanera" which marks the first appearance of Daisy, Dora's cousin, who celebrates her 15th birthday, a milestone in Latin culture.
tagline: Join Dora, her family, and her friends for these fiestas!
title: Dora the Explorer: It's a Party
